Pharmacy Systems Trainer
01 May 2014 02:44 PM - UAE
Pharmacy Systems Trainer Abu Dhabi, United Arab Emirate One of the worlds leading System Integrators is looking for a Pharmacy System Trainer to work in Abu Dhabi on a 7 month extendable contract. You will be responsible for development, and delivery of training materials and training environments for the Epic Willow Inpatient/Ambulatory application, and will be expected to demonstrate mastery of Epic software, mastery of Carefusion products, mastery of adult learning principles, and knowledge of best practices for developing and delivering instructor-led courses. You will need to be Certified in Epic Willow Inpatient/Ambulatory, have proven ability to produce training curriculum for Epic Willow Inpatient/Ambulatory, also prior experience designing and delivering Pyxis and Pharmogistics training. You will need 7+ years training delivery experience in a healthcare context, information systems, or certification as a technical trainer. As well as experience developing applied technology training curriculum in a health care, clinic or hospital environment. Please APPLY NOW with your current CV. This is an URGENT requirement. The client will conduct INTERVIEWS IMMEDIATELY for suitable candidates. All relevant applications will receive my INSTANT ATTENTION. For further information contact Simon Boxall on +44 208 254 7462 or simonboxall@pentaconsulting.com Penta Consulting is a global staffing solutions business providing innovative and flexible recruitment strategies for clients and the very best permanent, interim and contract career opportunities for candidates across IT & Telecoms. Ranked 8 in the 2013 Sunday Times Top 100 Companies to Work For awards, Penta holds a Queen's Award for (more...)
